### Welcome to the GitHub site for [Stoic Programmer ™](http://www.stoicprogrammer.com/)
All code samples appearing on Stoic Programmer™ will be hosted here on GitHub.
There may also be bonus code or other projects on the site as we progress in developing our content.
Please contact the site author and owner if additional information is required.
Please note that membership is by invite only.
##This site is run by Nicholas Ustick (@Nicholas-Ustick)
